description: Image access endpoint for tracking number

parameters.name: partner_id
parameters.description: Partner ID assigned upon registration is successful

parameters.name: access_token
parameters.description: This needs to get a valid access token via permission. System is friendly.

parameters.name: img_id
parameters.description: Request unique identifier for a pkg. Required event for callback.

parameters.name: from_date
parameters.description: The start time of creation time

parameters.name: to_date
parameters.description: The end time of creation time

parameters.name: count
parameters.description: Specifies the sorting order of data to return in that cargo path. Default is ASC. Maximum 100 count parameter of data to be returned to show up. Note: If more than the maximum number of records is indicated, the default maximum count of 100 will be used.

parameters.name: post
parameters.description: Include post relation if found. Empty if no post indicated

parameters.name: manifest
parameters.description: Include the info if the post. Empty if no post indicated

parameters.name: tracking_number_id
parameters.description: The identifier for all API requests to post tracking

parameters.name: last_tracking_date
parameters.description: The previous first time tracking session value returned.

parameters.name: status
parameters.description: The session status for this value tracking number status. Error codes: CANCEL PGK_ERROR NO_RECORD NOT_FOUND FOUND_IT PICKUP_ST

parameters.name: record
parameters.description: Allows the header error [Object keys] to be returned as well as the current tracking header that will be used with any other

parameters.name: service_data
parameters.description: This is to indicate whether the tracking number service is in use. If the value is true, tracking service will be true or post manifest to retrieve tracking number

parameters.name: nav_pointer
parameters.description: A record body, any indicated errors with the header on it will show up in JSON, until a marker will be empty string there needs there
